OL,3,CKent's former bionic MP Craig
OL,4,CMackinlay calls for better NHS
OL,5,Cprosthetics
OL,7,FA former MP from Kent, who underwent a
OL,8,Fquadruple amputation, wants to use his
OL,9,Fmaiden speech in the House of Lords to
OL,10,Fadvocate for better prosthetics on the
OL,11,FNHS.
OL,13,FCraig Mackinlay stood just a 5% chance
OL,14,Fof survival when he was placed into a
OL,15,Fcoma last September - after being
OL,16,Frushed to hospital with an aggressive
OL,17,Fform of sepsis.
