OL,5,Cprosthetics
OL,7,FTen months on and concentrating on his
OL,8,Frehabilitation - before he is sworn in
OL,9,Fas Lord Mackinlay of Richborough -
OL,10,FCraig hopes he can become a leading
OL,11,Fvoice for amputees.
OL,13,F"If you end up like this, you want to
OL,14,Fget back on to a life track as soon as
OL,15,Fyou possibly can.
OL,17,F"I'm sorry to say, I don't think the
OL,18,Foriginal prosthetic hands the NHS
OL,19,Fprovides do that," Craig told ITV
OL,20,FMeridian.
