OL,3,CKent's former bionic MP Craig
OL,4,CMackinlay calls for better NHS
OL,5,Cprosthetics
OL,7,F"A bionic arm like mine costs around
OL,8,F#50,000. The NHS will give you these,
OL,9,Fbut you might have to wait three years
OL,10,Ffor it. Surely it's less than the skin
OL,11,Fof the custard of the NHS budget,
OL,12,Flet's get on and provide these for
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,15,F"It makes you feel like a human again."
OL,17,FThe suddenness of the general
OL,18,Felection, just a day after his
OL,19,Femphatic return to parliament, meant
OL,20,Fthe former South Thanet MP decided not
OL,21,Fto seek re-election.
