OL,3,CKent's former bionic MP Craig
OL,4,CMackinlay calls for better NHS
OL,5,Cprosthetics
OL,7,FInstead, Craig was given a peerage in
OL,8,Fthe House of Lords in one of Rishi
OL,9,FSunak's final acts as Prime Minister -
OL,10,Fenabling him to continue his political
OL,11,Fcareer with a platform he wants to use
OL,12,Fto campaign on several issues,
OL,13,Fincluding raising awareness of the
OL,14,Fsymptoms of sepsis.
OL,16,FHe said: "Often it's you haven't
OL,17,Fpassed water for a whole day. There
OL,18,Fwill be vital signs: your temperature,
OL,19,Fyour blood pressure and all of that
OL,20,Fwill start to be going wrong.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
