OL,3,CKent's former bionic MP Craig
OL,4,CMackinlay calls for better NHS
OL,5,Cprosthetics
OL,7,F"You will be feeling the worst that
OL,8,Fyou've ever felt in the whole of your
OL,9,Flife. You need someone to recognise
OL,10,Fthat, get you to the hospital and get
OL,11,Fyou on the antibiotics to try to stop
OL,12,Fthe worst effects."
OL,14,FThe former Conservative MP is calling
OL,15,Fon health professionals to develop a
OL,16,FCOVID-19 style test to recognise the
OL,17,Fearly signs of the condition.
OL,19,FCraig will make his maiden speech in
OL,20,Fthe House of Lords later this year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
