OL,4,CMackinlay calls for better NHS
OL,5,Cprosthetics
OL,7,F"It gives me, you know, a chance to
OL,8,Fcontinue my political career that was,
OL,9,Fyou know, sadly cut short.
OL,11,F"I'll never know whether I might have
OL,12,Fwon that election. But, that doesn't
OL,13,Fmatter now. I've got a voice at the
OL,14,FRed End and I will use it."
