OL,3,CKent's former bionic MP Craig
OL,4,CMackinlay calls for better NHS
OL,5,Cprosthetics
OL,7,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "The NHS
OL,8,Fprovides a comprehensive package of
OL,9,Fcare and support for people who have
OL,10,Flost limbs, including a range of
OL,11,Fprosthetics. Bionic arms have been
OL,12,Fpart of the offer since 2022, and we
OL,13,Fare looking at the clinical criteria
OL,14,Fto see whether more patients could
OL,15,Faccess them quicker if their care
OL,16,Fteams think they would benefit."
